lyrics:
[Verse]
Late at night, I'm lost in the sound
Of all these small things that I have found
In this crazy world, we try to hide
Our truest selves, on this roller coaster ride

[Chorus]
But I know, deep inside, it's those small things
That make life worth living, make our hearts sing
In the chaos and the rush, we forget to see
The beauty of the small things, set our souls free
